        "### Feature Selection based on Correlation\n",
        "\n",
        "Now that we have the correlation matrix, we can use it to select features. We will primarily look for features that are highly correlated with our target variable, `popularity_capped`, and identify features that are highly correlated with each other (multicollinearity) to potentially remove redundant ones."
      ]
    },
